                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880227-87-off429 t17880227-87-cd430"></join>, a base metal watch, value 30 s. a silk watch-ribbon, value 1 d. a base metal watch-key, value 1 d. and a guinea in monies numbered
