                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I took charge of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I know nothing of it; I never was in the gentleman's company that I know of.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17880227-87-verdict431" type="verdictDescription">
